title: Amazon Best Books of the Month June 2018 [epub]
description:
Amazon: Best Books of the Month – June 2018



Hand-picked reads from the Amazon Books Editors. For anyone looking for a good book to read on your couch or the subway, this list is a good place to start your search.

List:
01. Calypso by David Sedaris
02. There There by Tommy Orange
03. The Book of M by Peng Shepherd
04. Florida by Lauren Groff
05. She Has Her Mother’s Laugh by Carl Zimmer
06. When Life Gives You Lululemons by Lauren Weisberger
07. Frenemies by Ken Auletta
08. Invitation to a Bonfire by Adrienne Celt
09. Kudos by Rachel Cusk
10. Room to Dream by David Lynch and Kristine McKenna
